1560    /**
1561     * builds Cart with checking for non-null required values
1562     * @return Cart
1563     */
1564    public Cart build() {
1565        Objects.requireNonNull(id, Cart.class + ": id is missing");
1566        Objects.requireNonNull(version, Cart.class + ": version is missing");
1567        Objects.requireNonNull(createdAt, Cart.class + ": createdAt is missing");
1568        Objects.requireNonNull(lastModifiedAt, Cart.class + ": lastModifiedAt is missing");
1569        Objects.requireNonNull(lineItems, Cart.class + ": lineItems is missing");
1570        Objects.requireNonNull(customLineItems, Cart.class + ": customLineItems is missing");
1571        Objects.requireNonNull(totalPrice, Cart.class + ": totalPrice is missing");
1572        Objects.requireNonNull(taxMode, Cart.class + ": taxMode is missing");
1573        Objects.requireNonNull(taxRoundingMode, Cart.class + ": taxRoundingMode is missing");
1574        Objects.requireNonNull(taxCalculationMode, Cart.class + ": taxCalculationMode is missing");
1575        Objects.requireNonNull(inventoryMode, Cart.class + ": inventoryMode is missing");
1576        Objects.requireNonNull(cartState, Cart.class + ": cartState is missing");
1577        Objects.requireNonNull(shippingMode, Cart.class + ": shippingMode is missing");
1578        Objects.requireNonNull(shipping, Cart.class + ": shipping is missing");
1579        Objects.requireNonNull(itemShippingAddresses, Cart.class + ": itemShippingAddresses is missing");
1580        Objects.requireNonNull(discountCodes, Cart.class + ": discountCodes is missing");
1581        Objects.requireNonNull(directDiscounts, Cart.class + ": directDiscounts is missing");
1582        Objects.requireNonNull(refusedGifts, Cart.class + ": refusedGifts is missing");
1583        Objects.requireNonNull(origin, Cart.class + ": origin is missing");
1584        return new CartImpl(id, version, createdAt, lastModifiedAt, key, customerId, customerEmail, customerGroup,
1585            anonymousId, businessUnit, store, lineItems, customLineItems, totalLineItemQuantity, totalPrice, taxedPrice,
1586            taxedShippingPrice, taxMode, taxRoundingMode, taxCalculationMode, inventoryMode, cartState, billingAddress,
1587            shippingAddress, shippingMode, shippingInfo, shipping, shippingRateInput, itemShippingAddresses,
1588            discountCodes, directDiscounts, refusedGifts, paymentInfo, country, locale, origin, custom,
1589            deleteDaysAfterLastModification, lastModifiedBy, createdBy);
1590    }

1634        builder.totalPrice = template.getTotalPrice();
1635        builder.taxedPrice = template.getTaxedPrice();
1636        builder.taxedShippingPrice = template.getTaxedShippingPrice();
